#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/live/landing_live/faq.html.heex:50
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Yes, the software is 100% free and open source (MIT). If you run your own "
"server, you only pay for hosting (a $5/month VPS is enough)."
msgstr ""
"Ja, de software is 100% gratis en open source (MIT). Als je je eigen server "
"draait, betaal je alleen voor hosting (een $5/month VPS is genoeg)."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/live/landing_live/faq.html.heex:95
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Yes. Server connections use HTTPS/WSS with TLS encryption. P2P calls are "
"encrypted end-to-end via DTLS-SRTP (built into WebRTC). Passwords are hashed"
" with bcrypt. And the code is open source &mdash; anyone can audit it for "
"vulnerabilities."
msgstr ""
"Ja. Serververbindingen gebruiken HTTPS/WSS met TLS-versleuteling. "
"P2P-gesprekken worden versleuteld end-to-end via DTLS-SRTP (ingebouwd in "
"WebRTC). Wachtwoorden zijn gehashed met bcrypt. En de code is open source "
"&mdash; iedereen kan het controleren op kwetsbaarheden."

